She caught Perceptor's smile out of the corner of her optics. "I am
glad to hear it. You are a very gifted bot."  She took in a deep
breath. "Please introduce me to your leader.  I wish to thank him for
sending you to protect me as well as guide me here. I am sure he will
be very pleased  with your performance."
